videos.description: Vanderbilt's Wade Baldwin IV shows off that all his highlight reel dunks in the regular season translate into tournament play with a posterizing finish against Tennessee.
videos.headline: Baldwin posterizes Tennessee defender with monstrous dunk

videos.description: Vanderbilt's Wade Baldin goes coast-to-coast for what he thinks is the game-tying lay in but after video review he just barely doesn't get it off before the buzzer.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's game-tying shot doesn't beat the buzzer
